org.eclipse.papyrus.RobotML

Interface CameraSystem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CyberPhysicalSystem, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ImageSensorSystem, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, RoboticSystem, SensorSystem, System
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CameraSystemImpl

    public interface CameraSystem
extends ImageSensorSystem
    A representation of the model object 'Camera System'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Width
    • Height
    • Alpha u
    • Alpha v
    • U0
    • V0
    • Color format
    • Translate
    • Rotate

    See Also:
    RobotMLPackage.getCameraSystem()
